{"tid":1815110,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Momo親姐遭嗆「看不懂韓文」","createTime":"2020-01-07T09:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T14:48:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65dc6f1ca1b86c5e5e8e02a416cf5658cd05553e","tid":1815110,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團TWICE日籍成員Momo日前認愛大13歲偶像金希澈，她6日首度貼出手寫信4張向粉絲致歉，同時表達感謝，卻仍有部分網友不買單，跑到她親姐的Instagram留言暗酸「反正Momo親姐看不懂韓文」，充滿惡意的言論，令其他粉絲看不下去、出面制止。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4631/d4631576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4631%2Fd4631576.jpg&h=ad2f8e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Momo親姐的IG遭南韓不知名網友留言亂嗆。（圖／翻攝自Momo姐IG、fmkorea論壇）<br />\n<br />\nMomo日前認愛金希澈，大部分粉絲抱著祝福態度，但還是有少部分酸民不買單。近日，有網友在韓國論壇貼出Momo親姐IG遭一名南韓網友暗酸的文章，該名酸民攻擊Momo與金希澈交往年紀差太多，內容充滿不雅用詞，甚至用藐視的形容詞攻擊Momo及金希澈，以及不實謠傳Momo懷孕，最後嗆「反正Momo親姐看不懂韓文，這樣留言也可以」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4631/d4631577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4631%2Fd4631577.jpg&h=61858e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Momo與姊姊感情要好。（圖／翻攝自Momo姐IG）<br />\n<br />\n這則留言在韓網論壇引起討論，該名南韓網友遭砲轟「太超過了」、「SM、JYP有事做了，向他提告吧」、「金希澈一定會告你」、「這傢伙瘋了吧」，許多人紛紛站出來揚言替偶像提告，也有人直接到Momo親姐IG留言，替她加油打氣。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f78fe2664051adf00354e10779d5e166a9a64","tid":1815110,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"直接D<br />\n看不懂狗吠"},{"pid":"827c0a7b700150d129942956764f00eb6f157ab4","tid":1815110,"uid":7903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"呀導該該叫"},{"pid":"80b3bc5eb164f9d78658edb7376ddfdcd0a3f27c","tid":1815110,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"兩姊妹個樣差咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60665c85cee6f32ccbca2012b157e317da2c4a9","tid":1815110,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"molamola momosan🚬"},{"pid":"e56096ab1796674f4c24c22428df96c4f39de7d9","tid":1815110,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"想知啲人鬧momo同斷腳狗啲咩"},{"pid":"368be49fbb69df0137369c02fe379d837a44af9b","tid":1815110,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016f78fe2664051adf00354e10779d5e166a9a64","tid":1815110,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"直接D<br />\n看不懂狗吠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b2ce0aa0b329b30e7e842a8a4ef7ad3da391aa","tid":1815110,"uid":231908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"80b3bc5eb164f9d78658edb7376ddfdcd0a3f27c","tid":1815110,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"兩姊妹個樣差咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"一個係日本，一個係韓國，你明的。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc652f39032aac679cd3a0a0d5115b9aa353437","tid":1815110,"uid":341458,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/a